## ğŸ’» Software Features

### Button Functions:
| Action | Function | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| **Single Click** | Toggle LED | Turn current LED on/off |
| **Double Click** | Switch Control | Change between LED1 âŸ· LED2 |
| **Long Press** | Blink Mode | Current LED blinks every 200ms |

### Serial Output:
- Real-time status updates
- Button action logging
- Current control state display

## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites:
- PlatformIO IDE
- ESP32 DevKit v1
- Hardware components listed above

### Installation:
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/B2_Blink_2_led.git
cd B2_Blink_2_led

# Build project
pio run

# Upload to ESP32
pio run --target upload

# Monitor serial output
pio device monitor
```

